l:dependency.name: SCTMExecutor
l:dependency.l:description: This plug-in allows triggering executions on Micro Focus Silk Central 17.0 or later.

l:dependency.name: Axis Web Services
l:dependency.l:description: An implementation of the SOAP ("Simple Object Access Protocol") submission to W3C.

l:dependency.name: Google Guice - Core Library
l:dependency.l:description: Guice is a lightweight dependency injection framework for Java 6 and above

l:dependency.name: Commons Lang
l:dependency.l:description: Commons Lang, a package of Java utility classes for the classes that are in java.lang's hierarchy, or are considered to be so standard as to justify existence in java.lang.

l:dependency.name: Guava: Google Core Libraries for Java
l:dependency.l:description:
Guava is a suite of core and expanded libraries that include utility classes, google's collections, io classes, and much much more.
Guava has only one code dependency - javax.annotation, per the JSR-305 spec.

l:dependency.name: JDOM
l:dependency.l:description: JDOM is, quite simply, a Java representation of an XML document. JDOM provides a way to represent that document for easy and efficient reading, manipulation, and writing. It has a straightforward API, is a lightweight and fast, and is optimized for the Java programmer. It's an alternative to DOM and SAX, although it integrates well with both DOM and SAX.

l:dependency.name: Apache Commons Codec
l:dependency.l:description: The Apache Commons Codec package contains simple encoder and decoders for various formats such as Base64 and Hexadecimal. In addition to these widely used encoders and decoders, the codec package also maintains a collection of phonetic encoding utilities.

l:dependency.name: HttpClient
l:dependency.l:description: The HttpClient component supports the client-side of RFC 1945 (HTTP/1.0) and RFC 2616 (HTTP/1.1) , several related specifications (RFC 2109 (Cookies) , RFC 2617 (HTTP Authentication) , etc.), and provides a framework by which new request types (methods) or HTTP extensions can be created easily.
